<li>Graves, John. "Tobacco that is not Smoked" in <i>From a Limestone Ledge</i> (the sections on snuff and chewing tobacco) <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0394512383" class="internal">ISBN 0-394-51238-3</a></li>
<li>Grehan, James. “Smoking and “Early Modern” Sociability: The Great Tobacco Debate in the Ottoman Middle East (Seventeenth to Eighteenth Centuries)”. <i>The American Historical Review, Vol. III, Issue 5</i>. 2006. 22 March 2008 <a href="http://www.historycooperative.org.myaccess.library.utoronto.ca/journals/ahr/111.5/grehan.html" class="external free" title="http://www.historycooperative.org.myaccess.library.utoronto.ca/journals/ahr/111.5/grehan.html" rel="nofollow">http://www.historycooperative.org.myaccess.library.utoronto.ca/journals/ahr/111.5/grehan.html</a></li>
